### Rules

for_window [app_id="factorio" class="factorio"] move window to workspace number 3
for_window [app_id = "discord" class="discord"] move window to workspace number 4
for_window [app_id="obs"] move window to workspace number 4
for_window [title="kitty-floating"] floating enable; resize set width 1000px; resize set height 700px

